
FRIEND FUNCTION

* It is not a member function of a class to which it is a FRIEND
* It declared in the class using friend class keyword.
* It must be defined outside the class to which it is friend.
* It can access any member of class which it is  friend.
* It can`t access memberof class directly.
* It has no caller object.
* It should not be defined using membership label (::).
* FRIEND FUNCTION can become to more than 1 class.
* FRIEND FUNCTION name can be same in every class.
* FRIEND FUNCTION can be declared inside the class as public or private. It doesn`t matter what we declared